  "siteName": "新智元",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"245\" data-backw=\"578\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb3fuo8ZMibEuSgehEy15NI5qKyd9KBlrJsj41K8aujZzS27ZljibAkXwWHgnAw93hBzwIEBE8P7AkLg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-imgfileid=\"505180398\" data-ratio=\"0.42421875\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=53289e92&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3fuo8ZMibEuSgehEy15NI5qKyd9KBlrJsj41K8aujZzS27ZljibAkXwWHgnAw93hBzwIEBE8P7AkLg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：倾倾</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">别再看「鉴AI攻略」了！当AI学会故意写错别字、流露人味，我们的直觉早已全线崩盘。这不只是技术的进化，更是一场关于平庸的生存危机。AI正在拼命演人，而我们却在越活越像机器。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">最近我发现，在回复工作消息时，我下意识敲出的第一句话，竟然自带一股浓浓的「AI味」。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">细思极恐！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"422\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"476\" data-imgfileid=\"505175682\" data-ratio=\"0.750788643533123\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"634\" data-width=\"634\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=679af4c0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1P4hQ7icwjaUaJ0ooJmDa0DsNzXibKicuRo6wKpKqzAAmtToXUlsiaKpnxvicDc4fgZrULgJntwtIoMPw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" mpa-font-style=\"mkknvkh8o0l\" style=\"font-size: 13px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkknvkhf4nl\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">猜猜这张图里，哪一栏是手写的，哪一栏是AI生成的？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种「身份错位」越来越频繁。当我们还在拿着过时的「鉴AI攻略」，试图通过破折号、排比句去鉴别时，AI早就变了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它学会了故意写错别字，学会了讲啰嗦的废话，甚至学会了在字里行间流露出一丝恰到好处的「人味」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">最讽刺的是，AI拼命地学习如何像人，而我们却在日复一日的规则中，把自己活成了算法。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这到底是因为AI进化得太快，还是我们正在被它悄悄「驯化」？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">别再数破折号了！</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">「AI鉴别攻略」正在失效</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">很多人都觉得，鉴别AI还不简单吗？那种文风平庸、动不动就用「深入探讨」、「强调」的，准是机器人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">还有进阶技巧：看排比，AI最爱用排比句。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">后来才发现，这些根本不是什么AI特征，而是文字的「通病」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">排比句、术语、破折号，这些东西在真实写作里到处都是，很多时候只是因为它们省力、安全、不容易出错。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">所谓的「AI专属特征」，在人类的日常写作里随处可见。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1536\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1536\" data-height=\"1024\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"375\" data-imgfileid=\"505175683\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7343d510&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1P4hQ7icwjaUaJ0ooJmDa0DmnuB0zZjVOkeLicUsqNTibXibG0kr35g0CibVSK2TxazXfCtemTbLHeS9g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">更尴尬的是，连「专家」自己都打架。翻一翻Wikipedia:Signs of AI writing，就能发现，里面的建议自相矛盾到离谱：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一会儿说「重复多」是AI，一会儿又说「变化多」也AI。甚至连研发检测工具的公司自己都承认没法保证100%准确</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI也会进化。 既然你盯着「破折号」，那AI公司就干脆调低了破折号出现的频率。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这很像一场猫鼠游戏。当你知道猫是通过铃铛声来抓鼠时，老鼠已经学会了屏住呼吸。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">曾经的鉴别套路，反而更容易误伤那些认真写字、风格严谨的真朋友。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5628571428571428\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1400\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1400\" data-height=\"788\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"316\" data-imgfileid=\"505175684\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3addbf5d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1P4hQ7icwjaUaJ0ooJmDa0DjI3ujRRl9xThjRdVZlYDVqmeBXvjT4Qb7dgXcz7tIzhdCZC0oyOdQw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">我们相信的「人味」，其实并不可靠</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">人们总觉得，人类的文字里天然带着一种「温度」，这是芯片永远模仿不出来的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但有一个研究，戳破了我们的伪装——所谓的「温度」，可能只是一场「集体幻觉」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">上个月，有学者进行了一项大规模的民意调查，结果比想象中夸张得多：大多数人根本分不清一段旋律是人写的，还是AI生成的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在诗词歌赋领域，结果更让人挫败：匹兹堡大学的一项实验发现，当人们读完一首AI写的诗，他们更倾向于认为这是人类写的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25666666666666665\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"600\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"600\" data-height=\"154\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"144\" data-imgfileid=\"505175685\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=21cd8692&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1P4hQ7icwjaUaJ0ooJmDa0D4h1Ol9aMdX34HhBv1sahmDyjLqAAZNiaCDLJyD0LIZgFphibTnOUtSHQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">猜猜这两首诗，哪一首是人写的？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">询问参与者后，得到了一个很讽刺的答案：人类写的诗太超前、太怪异，反而不像人能写出来的东西；而AI写的更符合我们对好诗的刻板印象。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">即便是最敏锐的观察者，也难逃「直觉陷阱」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">有人分享了一次尴尬的经历：他曾花15分钟在WhatsApp上跟一个房产中介聊得热火朝天，觉得对方不仅专业，而且对他找房的需求充满了真诚的关怀。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但最后对方主动承认：其实我是机器人。那一刻，他愤怒又无力，好像刚刚那15分钟突然被人抽走了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">显然，直觉已经靠不住了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">当内容不再可信，只能回归人本身</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">既然AI连语气和情感都能模仿得天衣无缝，那我们到底该怎么鉴别？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">文章给出了一个极具启发性的思路：不要盯着「内容」，要盯着「上下文」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">别看他说了什么，要看他是什么样的人、在什么样的背景下说</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">文章里提到一个非常经典的案例：一位编辑抓到了AI写的假新闻，不是因为文笔烂，而是因为「作者」的人设突然崩了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一个履历显示长期在纽约媒体圈打拼的人，突然说自己住在多伦多，这种现实背景的违和，AI很难完美编织的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">「人造瑕疵」更需要特别警惕。如果你发现对方发来的消息里有几个错别字、或者语气略显粗鲁，别急着断定对方是真人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkkns0czjt7\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"2.1626187961985215\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"947\" height=\"1825\" style=\"width: 100%;background-color: transparent;\" width=\"854\" data-width=\"947\" data-height=\"2048\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"1215\" data-imgfileid=\"505175686\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0112e0a7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3GPr5ef2nr16IkZtBTTaib1iaa2Qb7wCgE8ACoKB1FY3mg4yPcdpTe1qKy8VicvQ1M3fTX9II0ic0HRw%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">有个「作家」因为忘了从书中移除AI提示被抓包</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">现在的AI早就学会了「自黑」来骗取你的信任。所以，想要成为真正的鉴别高手，还要看「风格的连贯性」：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">那个平时只发表情包的朋友，突然写了三段逻辑严密的感言？</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">那个说话风格极简的领导，突然开始用华丽的排比句？</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">那个 完美的房产中介，在半夜三点也能秒回你的问题？</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">以上想都不用想，统统pass！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI可以模拟出「人味」，但它很难模拟一个具体的、活生生的、有生活轨迹的人。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">文字可以完美，但凭空捏造逻辑和背景很容易出岔子。这才是鉴别AI的最高级手段。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 2em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">AI这面镜子，照出人类表达的荒芜</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为什么AI造出来的假，越来越难辨认？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">现状十分扎心：科技大厂为了赢得这场AI竞赛，正在极力抵制给内容加「水印」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562585969738652\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1454\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1454\" data-height=\"818\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"316\" data-imgfileid=\"505175687\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=30ca548f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1P4hQ7icwjaUaJ0ooJmDa0D9YianXlibLMPyJU2oWJlTFdhehpbBne6nc5d2QXUrJO12Z1veeNnnBPA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 13px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">AI生成内容上强加「人工标签」，颇具讽刺意味</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而监管的脚步，在利益面前总是显得迟缓。到最后，真假反而成了一种负担，每个人都只能对自己读到的东西负责。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但最值得我们深思的，其实是AI的「平庸」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为什么AI的话术总是千篇一律？是因为它学习的语料库，就是由我们亲手投喂的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">那是亿万篇辞藻堆砌的报告、毫无个性的通稿、为了正确而正确的话术。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI就像一面镜子，它反射出的，本质上是人类社会表达的「最大公约数」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"900\" data-height=\"600\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"375\" data-imgfileid=\"505175688\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6cd32dc1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb1P4hQ7icwjaUaJ0ooJmDa0DJZGZC34J6LiamAGJmEy5uC6epv3okPAzUfu6GicjMcA9WOraa6sN1ujw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当我们在职场里为了安全感而隐藏锋芒，为了不出错而套用模板时，我们已经在无意识中，把自己活成了一个算法。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">也许，我们不需要成为「鉴AI大师」，那些甚至有点冒犯的真话、那些带着体温的私人记忆、那些无法被概率预测的奇思妙想，是人和AI最大的区别。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">别急着把文字磨得太干净，有些瑕疵，正是它还属于人的证据。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://www.ft.com/content/b2ebb99a-cfea-465f-93ff-0ea8ed6bfac5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ft.com/content/b2ebb99a-cfea-465f-93ff-0ea8ed6bfac5</a></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章指出传统 AI 鉴别方法已失效，AI 正学会模仿“人味”，建议通过观察上下文和风格连贯性来鉴别 AI，并反思人类表达的平庸化。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章指出传统 AI 鉴别方法已失效，AI 正学会模仿“人味”，建议通过观察上下文和风格连贯性来鉴别 AI，并反思人类表达的平庸化。",
  "summary": "文章指出，传统鉴别 AI 生成内容的“攻略”（如数破折号、看排比句）已经失效。AI 正在通过故意写错别字、制造“人造瑕疵”、模仿人类情感和写作风格等方式，变得越来越难以辨认。研究表明，人们甚至可能更倾向于认为 AI 创作的诗歌是人类所写，因为它更符合刻板印象。文章强调，鉴别 AI 不应再聚焦于“内容”本身，而应转向“上下文”，观察创作者的人设、背景以及风格的连贯性。同时，文章也反思了 AI 这面镜子，映照出人类表达的平庸化，呼吁人们在被 AI“驯化”的过程中，保持真诚、带有“瑕疵”的个体表达，以区分于机器。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "传统的 AI 鉴别方法（如语法、排版特征）已失效。",
      "explanation": "随着 AI 的进化，它已能学会故意制造“瑕疵”，模仿人类的写作风格，使得通过表面特征来鉴别 AI 内容变得不可能。"
    },
    {
      "point": "人类对“人味”的直觉判断不可靠。",
      "explanation": "多项研究表明，人们在音乐、诗歌等领域难以区分人类和 AI 的作品，有时甚至认为 AI 作品更像人类创作，因为它们更符合刻板印象。"
    },
    {
      "point": "鉴别 AI 的重心应从内容转向上下文和人设的连贯性。",
      "explanation": "识别 AI 的关键在于观察创作者的背景信息、行为模式及风格是否前后一致，因为 AI 难以凭空编织出一个具体、完整的“人”。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 反映出人类表达的平庸化倾向。",
      "explanation": "AI 的训练数据源于人类社会的“均质化”表达，因此它像一面镜子，映照出人类为追求安全和效率而趋同的表达方式。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "AI 正在拼命演人，而我们却在越活越像机器。",
    "最讽刺的是，AI 拼命地学习如何像人，而我们却在日复一日的规则中，把自己活成了算法。",
    "不要盯着『内容』，要盯着『上下文』。",
    "AI 可以模拟出『人味』，但它很难模拟一个具体的、活生生的、有生活轨迹的人。",
    "当我们在职场里为了安全感而隐藏锋芒，为了不出错而套用模板时，我们已经在无意识中，把自己活成了一个算法。"
  ],
